criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients aged 1 days to 30 years who were diagnosed with diabetes according to the
             World Health Organization criteria;

          -  Gender is not limited.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Gestational diabetes mellitus;

          -  Patients with malignant tumor,cardiovascular disease and other interference with the
             results of the study of the disease.

          -  Patients are participating in any other clinical studies;
